1082
01:39:22,830 --> 01:39:25,700
一直都没有人知道谁才是米瑟瑞的生父？
nobody knew who Misery's real father was?

1083
01:39:25,790 --> 01:39:28,330
或者他们能否重聚？
Or if they'd ever be reunited?

1084
01:39:28,420 --> 01:39:29,920
答案全部都在这里
It's all right here.

1085
01:39:30,000 --> 01:39:33,880
她最终是嫁给伊安，还是温德松？
Does she finally marry Ian, or will it be Windthorne?

1086
01:39:33,960 --> 01:39:35,760
也全都在这里
It's all right here.

